:1545875265,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e就可以直接博士生毕业。不，可以直接评上教授。不，可以直接拿菲尔兹奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不，这不可能。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562662642,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562662642","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546132353,"updated_time":1546298953,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e20181230，我觉得楼主低估了哥猜的难度，证明出来哪里还需要读清华北大啊\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我以为，中学生证明了哥猜，这辈子就可以演讲、吃喝玩乐了。读大学的一个功能是就业，而证明了哥猜完全不需要考虑就业的问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年轻人证明哥猜，就好比他爸爸告诉他其实不是亲生的，真正亲生的父母是亿万富豪，而且只有他一个子女，就等着继承财产。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e中学生证明出来，估计在现存知乎的聪明人也是数一数二，甚至人类也排的上号。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e自己想想吧！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果中学生，建议证明一下如下猜想：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果x^x=x^^2，试证  x^^2=y 和 y^^0.5=x 等价。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个东西更有价值，因为可能x^^^0.5更有趣！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561017728,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"838548543ed805c948eae5457cca200c","url_token":"yu-fei-yang-55-89","name":"只微寒","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-36bd773b15281bb25d670d157562dc5b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-36bd773b15281bb25d670d157562dc5b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/838548543ed805c948eae5457cca200c","user_type":"people","headline":"已退役MO被虐玩家","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561017728","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545907935,"updated_time":1545907935,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e反对那个高赞的自称是题主老师的回答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e能有给出哥猜的“不完整证明”的知识储备与对知识的理解能力的人 竟然是一个在数列上下很大功夫的学生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e能进行审稿并指出哪里是证明关键的人 居然在一个高中当竞赛教练\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e时代真是变了啊\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561710084,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1f2bc82fe9e49fee739cd79ac9ff18a5","url_token":"sun-yan-88-83","name":"材料劝退委员会","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0739c9d7acf3aed74ca2874893f45e1d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0739c9d7acf3aed74ca2874893f45e1d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1f2bc82fe9e49fee739cd79ac9ff18a5","user_type":"people","headline":"承接各路咨询：高考报告，读研读博，职业发展，情感问题","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561710084","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545991550,"updated_time":1545991550,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":12,"content":"\u003cp\u003e在上清华北大之前你还需要证明很多东西\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你先证明你证明了哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你再证明你能证明你证明了哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你再证明你在证明你能证明你证明了哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等这些都证明完\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后证明一下你是你\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后就可以保送清北数学系了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563855250,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"38fd1f8e97de27b5d9fc6ba74168bd02","url_token":"lu-ha-hua","name":"鲁哈花","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/ecfa3a89c645daad632756187ea1c4e4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/ecfa3a89c645daad632756187ea1c4e4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/38fd1f8e97de27b5d9fc6ba74168bd02","user_type":"people","headline":"进步使人难过","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563855250","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546302906,"updated_time":1546302906,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e“如果”，题目中提到“如果”，也就是说假设这是真的（不探讨是否是真的），被保送是小case。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当年陈景润证明了“1+2”，随着报告文学《哥德巴赫猜想》火遍大江南北，陈景润获得英雄般的荣誉，各种破格晋升接踵而至，研究员，人大代表，中央接见，出国访问，中科院院士，杂志主编等，组织上还给解决了个人问题，相信也得到了一流的医疗资源。陈景润完成这些的时候早已大学毕业，因此无法再将其擢升为大学生了，是不是好遗憾。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而陈景润做了什么贡献呢，就是1+2。是利用一种逼近的思路从9+9，6+6，。。。，1+3，1+2一路做过来的最好成果，下一步就是哥德巴赫猜想（1+1）了。但最新的学术意见认为，1+2和1+1之间，存在巨大的差距，已经达到了传统方法的极限，更进一步需要新的革命性的数学工具（在高中生未成名之前，我一个爱好者只能“被迫”选择相信这批卓越地位的数学家的言论）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么说吧，哥德巴赫猜想是100分，那么9+9是25分，1+2从25分一路改进到了50分。我们的高中生从50分提升到了100分。仅凭这一点，同为破解希尔伯特问题成功者的一员，已经和怀尔斯（费马大定理），佩雷尔曼（庞加莱猜想）肩并肩了，远超陈景润，一个高中生超过40的可能性不大，收获菲尔兹奖板上钉钉，而且顺便打破最年轻获奖者记录。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果说怀尔斯，佩雷尔曼在公众印象中是一个单纯的难题破解者，我们的高中生则大大不同。前文说过，证明1+1需要新的数学工具，既然已经“如果”了，那么新的数学工具想必也一定诞生了，这才是更甚于\u003cb\u003e哥德巴赫-高中生名字定理\u003c/b\u003e的数学财富，必将引领一场或大或小的革命。这时候，我们的高中生就已经比肩欧几里得，欧拉，高斯，黎曼，牛顿，莱布尼茨等人了，很可能迫使数学家祖师爷前十排名发声变动，并顺便填补当代超级大师级数学家的空白。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说到这里还提保送就庸俗了，您可以发声质疑传统教育制度了，提出您的“钱学森之问”，教育部长肯定急一头汗。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这一切的发声都只需要让最开始的“如果”二字成真就可以了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559963535,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2633deb3f6b222f3f0664d958a7ac3c6","url_token":"si-kao-shi-guang-de-nan-ren","name":"思考时光的鱼","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-23ffedddea353a809047369ba554427c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-23ffedddea353a809047369ba554427c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2633deb3f6b222f3f0664d958a7ac3c6","user_type":"people","headline":"数学工作者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559963535","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545797144,"updated_time":1545882009,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e楼主低估了哥德巴赫猜想的影响力了。如果高中生证明了歌德巴赫猜想，不会被清华北大数学系保送，应该会被清华北大数学系竞相聘用为教授。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560492710,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7b6772f7ba77dbfa1860b9961c503a16","url_token":"ji-ze-ming-72-53","name":"VEDA","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e18b7e531bccf437b8e2dfb8dfee6ef6_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e18b7e531bccf437b8e2dfb8dfee6ef6_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7b6772f7ba77dbfa1860b9961c503a16","user_type":"people","headline":"大学狗","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560492710","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-40119bbd22cc862a1ce71296fc14e45f_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545842545,"updated_time":1545842545,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我寻思这位小老弟花三个月完全掌握了数学\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ace002ceb5f449cc9643c9fc070f4c93_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"531\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2dffbb95ad99fb110c8b120c79858ac5_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ace002ceb5f449cc9643c9fc070f4c93_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='531'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"531\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2dffbb95ad99fb110c8b120c79858ac5_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ace002ceb5f449cc9643c9fc070f4c93_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ace002ceb5f449cc9643c9fc070f4c93_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559411270,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"dd0779ef0398be79527612f01c351233","url_token":"ceng-xi-wen-36","name":"曾玺文","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1570d58e5d2cacc86bc8e3d9781ba54a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1570d58e5d2cacc86bc8e3d9781ba54a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/dd0779ef0398be79527612f01c351233","user_type":"people","headline":"三本菜鸡","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559411270","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545724686,"updated_time":1545725218,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":129,"content":"\u003cp\u003e支持楼主，没有问题的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我高中时就自发研究证明了费马大定理。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我当时想到了一个绝妙的证明方法，可惜这里地方太小……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e话说清华北大数学系居然都不给我发录取邀请，气死我了\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了题主给其他人的回复，才意识到这tm不是高中生，而是个高中学历的民科啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不皮了，我本来还想耍个机灵。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e您……算了我也没什么好说的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e人类历史上一个一个的突破，都是积累了足够的技术沉淀，厚积薄发而出的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不要总是妄想自己一个人去挑战全世界。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真实世界不是小说。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560533941,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c38f75e73003c034b2f5b1525e1d2738","url_token":"hayashiretsu","name":"医龙烈风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e2741632528d8f97ae21d9b7e59b4557_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e2741632528d8f97ae21d9b7e59b4557_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c38f75e73003c034b2f5b1525e1d2738","user_type":"people","headline":"热爱解剖的疯子","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560533941","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545851501,"updated_time":1545851501,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":21,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不请自来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e翻了几个回答就不想再翻了。一是看不懂，二是戾气太重，有些还所问非所答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先说结论：会，而且远不止。不过天才去接受清北高等教育在知识层面上基本没必要了，尤其是去学数学。大神 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\" data-hash=\"298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\"\u003e@数学建模老司机\u003c/a\u003e 的回答看起来很靠谱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e某些“优秀人才”是通过怀疑和蔑视他人收获高高在上的存在感，只能说教育于你而言实为浪费。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不知道的如果想回答直接摆出清北招生办电话让题主自己联系询问就好了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知道的不是让你来论述猜想多难多不切实际的，你觉得你泼冷水是好心是负责任是忠言逆耳，\u003cb\u003e你算老几？随随便便负责他人的人生？家长和老师会不知道学生现状吗？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学大神真要提出学习建议的，扼要说明必须的最低知识储备，可能的话介绍一些相关书籍和资料就够了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真的看不懂会知难而退的，其它多余的废话用不着你多说，全世界不是只有你一个人聪明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺便有人说投机？还是沽名钓誉？可以说非常可笑了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证不出来钓个毛线的誉哦！你是会安慰人家送人家小花花还是谢谢参与奖状？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证出来了这点荣誉算毛线哦！你是觉得ta配不上你更聪明更优秀吗，麻烦你去证一个。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561320445,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"186b7e85be8226291b46ab24c9cb5fa5","url_token":"wang-xiao-fei-46-85","name":"白城星夜","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/3831d2c8f320c9ac029680542b41a6be_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/3831d2c8f320c9ac029680542b41a6be_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/186b7e85be8226291b46ab24c9cb5fa5","user_type":"people","headline":"暴黑，无恋爱史，每年只看两部番","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561320445","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545958640,"updated_time":1545958640,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e真证出来你可以直接去清华北大数学系给那些保送生上课了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562548554,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562548554","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546099187,"updated_time":1546099187,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e❤️守护全世界最好的证明❤️\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e用户：证明\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e动态：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e7个月前:问“已知四面体四个面面积，如何求体积？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4个月前:询问“河北大学数学系信息？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3个月前:赞同“5秒计算错位相减。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3个月前:赞同“四面体体积公式！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2天后：发布“证明哥德巴赫猜想论文”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果奇迹有过程，那一定是证明！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559455803,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"01da282cd54fa04dc75643944d8b43bb","url_token":"gao-san-gou-67-76","name":"肖明浩BIT","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04af9d8966ecf44558e55a787b6ab92f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04af9d8966ecf44558e55a787b6ab92f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/01da282cd54fa04dc75643944d8b43bb","user_type":"people","headline":"略带低级趣味的理工男","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559455803","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545728379,"updated_time":1545908915,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":57,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我先在这里mark一下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e按照我的能力，我是没资格来谈论哥德巴赫猜想的证明的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想说几句别的:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主身为一个高中生拥有证明哥德巴赫猜想的能力的话，我想你不必现在还在纠结会不会被清北的数院保送的问题。你现在应该已经可以拿到IMO金牌了吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对了最后补充一句，T大的数院不如P大的。如果是真的，去MIT都是屈才。所以我推荐你去中科大，和贱贱老师 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/789a006980ffe4e7d86594fd2c21c927\" data-hash=\"789a006980ffe4e7d86594fd2c21c927\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$789a006980ffe4e7d86594fd2c21c927\"\u003e@贱贱\u003c/a\u003e 称兄道弟。我也推荐你去山东某世界一流大学（副部级）的泰山学堂，世一大（副部级）的数学系全国知名，你值得拥有。详情请咨询邓总 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/47ac97a287b10d41ef3239f61ea08920\" data-hash=\"47ac97a287b10d41ef3239f61ea08920\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$47ac97a287b10d41ef3239f61ea08920\"\u003e@邓铂鋆\u003c/a\u003e （狗头保命）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是我觉得这是假的，我把话放在哪里这里，欢迎明年1月1日来打脸。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对了，论文发在知乎上面你不觉得太可惜了吗？不得发在微博这种用户更多的平台吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，我严肃说一下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我希望以后不要在知乎上看见这种问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53405629\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-18a4e4f21513c06dc69b04d807afbccf_r.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1034\" data-image-height=\"1128\" class=\"internal\"\u003e肖明浩BIT：民科还是天才，这是一个问题\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561001864,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"aa7a6d47080002b7865b9713d9a36900","url_token":"a-xian-99-18","name":"阿线","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8bb5b7c550ebba98e80b45706797cd5e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8bb5b7c550ebba98e80b45706797cd5e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/aa7a6d47080002b7865b9713d9a36900","user_type":"people","headline":"爱好是卖弄渊博 特长是故步自封","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561001864","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545906256,"updated_time":1545919975,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e没有人在沽名钓誉哗众取宠的时候认为自己的确在沽名钓誉哗众取宠。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（经热心网友提醒，除了营销号\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560812117,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3010ca1527032ee54f643d1597fa0037","url_token":"shuang-dao-ru-ye-qin-wu-yuan","name":"Rachel","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b1a01958845c1d4bb707ccb6fe519c93_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b1a01958845c1d4bb707ccb6fe519c93_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3010ca1527032ee54f643d1597fa0037","user_type":"people","headline":"不懂数学的数学系学生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560812117","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545890101,"updated_time":1545890331,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e同学你好\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  倘若你真能证明出哥德巴赫猜想……不说清华北大，国内外任何一所知名大学聘请你为教授都不为过。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，就我在数学系学习的一些经验来看，以中学知识证明哥德巴赫猜想是\u003cb\u003e绝对不可能的事情。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望答主不要做无用功，把准备高考的时间全部用在这些对你现阶段毫无意义的事。哥德巴赫猜想的意思我想但凡初中的学生都可以理解该猜想说的是什么，但是以中学知识加上粗略的高等数学知识去证明哥德巴赫猜想…用陈景润先生的一句话，叫做\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e骑着自行车上月球。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在最主要的任务是准备高考，如果对数学科研有兴趣，完全可以进入大学数学系后，进行系统、专业的学习。以后在一步步的走向科研这条路，而不是将大把大把的时间与精力全部浪费在这条歪路上，错过本该正确的路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能有些数学专业的答主说的话你会不喜欢听，但是他们说的是很正确的，你必须先想办法进入数学系，然后在考虑这个问题。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561464483,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5be040c7edb6ee5ba769cf5f737b1ba9","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561464483","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545969661,"updated_time":1546177216,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你这么聪明完全可以通过直接参加高考考上清华北大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么对保送这么有执念呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e既然对哥猜这么感兴趣，反正已经二百七十来年没人能证明了，你等高考完，考上北大清华再证明或者发布你的结果也不晚啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e着什么急呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562017031,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bdca69bf8c66074dddc1145f4f0de0f0","url_token":"li-jia-89-55","name":"李嘉","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f37e0a9922774c58ab394cc1e68531af_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f37e0a9922774c58ab394cc1e68531af_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bdca69bf8c66074dddc1145f4f0de0f0","user_type":"people","headline":"不要轻易给人贴标签，拒绝制造传播焦虑","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562017031","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546046108,"updated_time":1546046108,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e最近读完了《Thinking，fast and slow》受益颇多。感觉可以从这本书出发通过人类认知的层面来分析这个问题背后反应的问题，而不是仅仅单纯停留在科学以及民科的角度出发：\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cb\u003e信息越少，人对自己的判断对事物的认知就越自信。人们总是更热衷于用已有的信息去解读或者脑补一个故事，而不是去积极寻找更多的信息和知识。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp\u003e举个例子：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e比如，前一段时间的大巴失控入水惨剧就是这样的例子。一开始的时候广大人民群众所获得的信息非常少，有不可靠消息源指出有女司机逆行造成大巴躲闪不及造成事故。当这个信息放出来以后，绝大多数人表现出了对这个单一信息的极大接受度，大众根据这个信息源迅速作出了判断——“又是女司机，难怪”。这个关于“女司机”的故事符合绝大多数人非理性思考的认知，这个又一起女司机引起的血案一下子在人们的脑袋里栩栩如生了。到后来，随着更多信息的不断出现，比如出事前视频信息，公共交通系统某些“知情人士”透露公交司机的一些灰色内部培训等等，人们掌握的信息量一下子多了很多。而这个时候，人们一下子不敢轻易做出判断了。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e再比如，我们常说的“所见即所得”和“耳听为虚，眼见为实”。但是在过去，我们一直依靠眼睛所能接受的信息深信地球是平的，深信地心说。后来，我们又学到了人类肉眼所见的只是可见光的极小一部分（可见光的信息量相比不可见光实在是太有限了）。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e回到这个题，我们需要理解这种信息量和认知自信的悖论对我们人类的普遍影响。如果只是停留在对于高中生或者民科的认知自信的结果的嘲讽，那么当我们遇到了超越我们认知边界的事物的时候（比如上文中我们一开始解读大巴落水事件的时候），我们往往也会犯这种错误。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e2. 大家对民科未经证伪的哗众取宠容忍度很高，反应了人们对于小概率事件往往过分夸大，而同时又大大低估了大概率事件的本质。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e同样举例子：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e购买彩票是个经典的小概率事件。有那么多的人为了中彩票概率从百万分之0变为百万分零点不惜花费大量的时间和金钱，远远高于内在的收益期望值。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e再比如，如果同时有两个消毒液，一个号称能够消灭98%的细菌，一个号称能够消灭99.9%的细菌。消费者往往会用远远高于收益的价格会购买后者，得到1.9%的效果提升，当与99.9%或者100%相比，98%就显得让人紧张，难以忍受。98%远远没有获得其应得的理性认知。不过，98%也别觉得委屈。实际上假如100%是存在的，99.9%都会被人们嗤之以鼻。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e回到主题，民科的哗众取宠，扬言能解读哥德巴赫猜想，本质上是个极低概率的小概率事件。很多支持民科的人对其容忍度很高，甚至为其辩解说“事情还没有完全展开，你怎么知道不能行”，本质上就是对于小概率事件的过分夸大，同时又对“未受高等教育是解决不了世界难题”这个极大概率事件的极度低估。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先写到这里。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560513264,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1edbfc751b304b53b6d4b6eb435a74a1","url_token":"paranoia-11-67","name":"paranoia12","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-24acbfb00112469f90d1408b03bbf035_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-24acbfb00112469f90d1408b03bbf035_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1edbfc751b304b53b6d4b6eb435a74a1","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560513264","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545845563,"updated_time":1545845563,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我看好你呀\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是如果这次的证明被专业人士指出存疑类的问题，那你就要乖乖准备高考好吗？咱大学还有大把的时间可以研究呀，不要让你的聪明因为社会而埋没。加油 \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563577454,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e945d2c4e15db77146e1b19ddb2fa6f9","url_token":"371293","name":"57005","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd7e1b989eacb89ee263629a8c7c2d1e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd7e1b989eacb89ee263629a8c7c2d1e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e945d2c4e15db77146e1b19ddb2fa6f9","user_type":"people","headline":"数学爱好者 SCP基金会粉","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563577454","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546252808,"updated_time":1546282838,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e毫无疑问，结束了。哪位大佬考虑出一下户籍啊（笑）。不过这个点子写SCP确实蛮不错的，对我还蛮有启发的，还是非常感谢这位证明哥德巴赫猜想的神人（笑）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e引用一段用在这里可能不太恰当的SCP的原文吧:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e诱惑总是存在，它也总是强大。我曾夜不能寐，思考着所有的懊悔，所有我做错的事。以几个怪梦为代价，我便能消去我所有的罪，重获新生。我的终结即是新生。\u003cbr\u003e不要去试。你所读到的不是一条逃脱之路，而是对基金会失败的证词。彻底、完全的失败，我们已经把它招至自身一次一次又一次。你做的是在毁灭那些无辜者，阻止他们出生，不让他们知道生命是什么。他们只会是记忆里的阴影，孤独时光里的零碎念想，来自那些可能曾经知道他们的人。\u003cbr\u003e如果这都还不够，那就记住：花园带来的安慰不是真的。那是逃避真实。我们都想回到一切是温暖、简单的时候，满是夏阳和翠草的时光。我们每个人都想重新沐浴在光明之下。但我们都做了自己的选择，我们都许下了自己的誓言。我们每个人都会在黑暗中死去，别无他法。\u003cbr\u003e——SCP-3997-我的终结即是新生\u003cbr\u003e（转载遵循CC-BY-SA协议，原文地址\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3997\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003escp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e/scp-3997\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e，作者Tufto）\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e————已归档的回答————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e谢邀，以这个为题材写了一篇SCP基金会的同人文……由于是同人文所以文笔比不上官网，希望dalao不要深究口语化玩烂梗之类的问题了……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————分隔线————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e项目编号：SCP-CN-(1+1)-EX-J\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e项目等级：我已经找到了一种绝妙的解法，但是空白太小我写不下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e已归档的收容措施：机动特遣队-丁丑-2^82589933－1“毕达哥斯拉”将监视研究SCP-CN-(1+1)-J的数学家，如有数学家有重大研究成果，立即对其施以A级记忆消除，必要时可直接处决。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e描述：SCP-CN-(1+1)-J为“任一大于2的偶数都可写成两个质数之和”这一数学命题，对有初等数论基础的人有轻度的成瘾性的模因影响，受影响者会尝试使用自己拥有的知识证明此命题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e鉴于SCP-033、SCP-3380的异常性质，基金会认为对SCP-CN-(1+1)-J的证明或证伪都会导致KKSK级“啊啊啊尤里卡！！”末日情景，这会使所有理解“数学”这一概念的人类脱光衣服在街上奔跑直至死亡。但鉴于证明或证伪SCP-CN-(1+1)-J的数学工具尚未被发明，因此只需要简单的收容措施即可。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e事件CN-(1+1)-J-A发生后，SCP-CN-(1+1)-J被证明，但预计中的末日并未发生，故项目重新分级为Explained。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e事件CN-(1+1)-J-A：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e20██年██月██日，基金会网络爬虫在日常的检查中发现在名为█乎的网站中一位名为“证明”的用户声称其证明了SCP-CN-(1+1)-J，基金会随即展开调查，在其电脑中发现了名为证明.txt的文件。经过检查，尽管此证明仅仅使用了高中知识，但确实严谨证明了哥德巴赫猜想。由于没有末日发生，该用户在发表证明后同时被北大清华邀请做客座教授，但最终被基金会人员秘密安排进入基金会就职。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e警告：基金会系统遭到入侵，以下内容可能拥有信息危害，不建议查看。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e仅限二、三、五、七……级人员查看：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只使用高中知识？这“证明”可真有趣，基金会已经懦弱到为了避免末日而启动“忽怠协议”，让所有人承认一个错误证明为真理了？然而，真理难道真的这么容易被埋没吗？——05-P，这里P指Prime\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————分隔线————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的态度是没抱什么期望了，但是所谓“证明”该看还是要看，万一打脸了这篇文我还是要改的（）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外也希望大佬们能给我的文提点建议，在这里提前感谢！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=240\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=200\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
